{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回\"中原一点红\"中，中原一点红这位昔年中原第一快剑杀手重现江湖。胡铁花向苏苏讲述了此人的来历——杀人如麻，剑法精准毒辣，仅以腕力发剑，一剑刺中咽喉天突穴，只沁一点鲜血。酒宴上，金老太太阐述了自己的\"格局论\"，并揭露了对抗兰花先生的计划：兰花先生利用苏苏、慕容和袖袖三人作饵，引诱楚留香现身，再由饵料反杀。楚留香明知是陷阱，仍坚持救援。众人虽已识破计划却按兵不动，以免三人被灭口。柳明秋的死是否另有隐情，成为谜团。楚留香的正义与坚持，与兰花先生精密算计的对决就此展开。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "有人",
      "listener": "char_zhong_yuan_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "只要有人肯出高价，什么人你都杀，甚至包括你最好的朋友在内，这是不是真的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_yuan_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "中原一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_yuan_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "中原一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我没有朋友可杀。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_yuan_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "中原一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我根本没有朋友。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "中原一点红?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "搜魂剑无影，中原一点红。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这个人真的就是昔年那个号称中原第一快剑，杀人不见血的一点红。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "这个人就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他还没有死?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "好像还没有，有种人好像很不容易死，想要他死的人能活着的反而不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他是不是也像楚香帅一样，装死装了一段日子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "现在他为什么又活回来了呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "当然是因为我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "是你把他找出来的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你找他出来干什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "若求杀人手，但寻一点红。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我找他出来，当然是为了杀人的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "人家要杀我们，我们也要杀他们，你说这是不是天公地道的事?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "一点红是什么意思?他全身上下连一点红的颜色都没有，别人为什么要叫他一点红?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "中原一点红的名字就是这样来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我也是楚留香的朋友，可是我从来不想为他复仇。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这一点我和胡铁花是完全不同的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为我根本不相信楚香帅会死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "她说她会看相。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "她看得出楚留香绝不是早死的相。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说的看相，并不是迷信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而是我看过的人太多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我相信每个人都有一种格局，也就是说，一种气质，一种气势，一种性格，一种智慧，这是与生俱来的，也是后天培养出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个高格局的人，就算运气再坏，也要比一个低格局的人运气最好时好得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "譬如说，一个挑肥的人运气最好的时候，最多只不过能够多挑几次水肥而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了我之外，我相信这个世界上一定还有另外一个人的想法和我一样，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个人一定也不相信楚香帅会这么容易就死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "这个人就是谋刺楚留香那个组织的首脑?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "他为什么不相信香帅已死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他一定是楚留香这一生中最大的一个仇敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个聪明人了解他的仇敌，一定要比了解他的朋友深刻得多，否则他就死定了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为一个人要害他的朋友是非常容易的，要害他的仇敌却很不容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以他一定要等到非常了解他的仇敌之后，才能伤害他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个最容易伤害到你的，通常都是最了解你的，这种人通常都是你最亲近的朋友。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "这个人是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "我的意思是说，这个组织的首脑是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "没有人知道他是谁!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我们最多也只不过能替他取一个代号。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "你们对这个人知道的有多少?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "没有多少。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我们只知道他是个非常精密深沉的人，和楚香帅之间有一种无法解开的仇恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "在这种情况下，我们对这个人根本就可以算是一无所知。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "但是你们却叫他兰花?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "你们为什么叫他兰花?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "这个人和兰花有什么关系?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "在这种情况下，我们可以确信，这位兰花先生对楚香帅的了解，一定远比我们深刻得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "因为一个人对仇敌的了解，一定远比对朋友的了解深刻得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的，",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上有很多事都是这样子的，我们不但要了解，而且要忍受。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "尤其是女人，女人的了解和温柔，对男人来说，有时远比利剑更有效。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人如果真的能对楚香帅了解得非常深刻，他就绝不会相信楚香帅会死得那么容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "就算江湖中人都确定楚香帅已经死了，他也不会相信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除非他亲眼看见了香帅的尸体。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "他要怎么样才能证实呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一点我们也想了很久，我相信我们的智慧也不比他差多少，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们也拟定了一个计划，来证实香帅的生死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们确信，只有用这一种方法，才能证实香帅的生死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "哪一种方法?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种方法虽然很复杂，可是只要用两个字就能说明。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "哪两个字?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "感情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个兰花先生既然对香帅如此了解，当然知道香帅是非常重感情的人，就算他已经决定不问江湖的恩怨仇杀，可是他如果听见有一个绝不能死的人陷入必死的危机，他一定会复出的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果他没有死，就一定会复出的，如果他还不出现，就可以断定他已经死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "要证明香帅的生死，这是不是最好的法子?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我相信你一定已经知道这个人是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三个人是不是要比一个人更保险得多?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "所以他们就找来了三个人，三个在老臭虫心目中都是绝不能死的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "这三个人其中就有一个是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以香帅刚刚才会说，他还没有死，其中有一部分原因是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兰花先生断定，只要你们三个人有了必死的危机，香帅就会复活。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是香帅如果已退隐，怎么会知道这个消息?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他当然一定先要把这件事造成一件轰动天下的大事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他当然也知道像老臭虫这样子，就算已经退隐了，耳朵还是比兔子还灵。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一点是很难做到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老臭虫一向比鬼还精。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "所以这位兰花先生一定要先把慕容身边的主力消灭，先置他于必败之地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们很早以前就已想到，这次计划中最大的阻力就是柳明秋柳先生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柳先生不死，慕容无死理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "所以他非死不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只不过天下江湖中人都知道，想要把柳先生置之于死地，并不比对付香帅容易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们相信他必有奇兵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "这一支奇兵是什么人呢?什么人能够杀柳先生于瞬息?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "我们都想不出这个人是谁，所以我们也拟定了一个计划。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们就选择了这个地方，就在这里等。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我才知道，我们这些人真是一群老狐狸。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "直到那时候为止，我们才彻底了解兰花先生这个计划。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他利用你们三个人作饵，来钓香帅这条大鱼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 419,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他算定香帅只要不死，就一定会去救你们，就算明知你们都是想要他命的人，他也一样会去救你们的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老臭虫这么样一个聪明的人，有时候却偏偏喜欢做些呆事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "这个计划中最重要的一点，当然就是要用什么方法，才能让楚留香死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一击当然要经过千筹百算，绝不能有一点错失。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "可是不论怎么算，这个世界上大概还没有人敢说能在一击之下，将楚留香搏杀于当地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除非出手的人是香帅绝对不会提防的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这一方面，慕容和袖袖当然是最好的人选了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 441
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "香帅去救他们，他们杀了香帅，就是告诉别人，也没人相信，大家只知道楚留香早已死了，在这一战的一年之前就已死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "你们既然已经识破了这个计划，为什么不直接揭它?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我们不敢轻举妄动。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "因为你们，你，慕容，和袖袖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "我不懂。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "计划如果被揭穿，你们三个也就没有利用的价值了，兰花随时都可能杀了你们泄愤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "所以香帅坚持我们不管有任何行动，都要先考虑你们的安全。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "无论在任何情况下，都不能让你们死在别人手里，就算明知你们是钓饵也一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不管怎么样，你们这件事还是做错了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "哪件事做错了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你们不该让柳先生死的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他也是人，也是你们的朋友，你们既然知道他是牺牲的目标，为什么还要让他死在我手里?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 495
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我相信你们也不能不承认，如果你们想救他，一定有机会，可是你们连试都没有试。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "你真是个奇怪的女孩子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "你自己杀了他，反而来怨我们。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 503
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "我只问你，我说的有没有理?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "有理，当然有理。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "只不过我也有几句话要问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "你问。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "柳先生为什么一定要选中你陪他去突袭?为什么要把你先带到这里来?为什么还要先为你制造一些让他自己心乱的机会?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我刚才好像已经说过，连我自己都开始对我们这些人觉得有点不满意了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为我们实在太精。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "有时候我甚至希望能被别人骗上一两次!",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可惜我们这些老狐狸还是有办不到的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "直到现在为止，我们对这位兰花先生还是一无所知，甚至连他是男是女都不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们只知道一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们一定会把他找出来的，不管他是个什么样的人，我们都会把他找出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在你们准备怎么做?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "现在我惟一要去做的事，还是那件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "去救慕容和袖袖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在这种情况下，你还是要去救他们?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们说说看，柳明秋的死，是不是另一种伪装?为了某种目的而设下的圈套?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "谁也不能回答你的问题。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_lao_tai_tai",
      "speaker_name": "金老太太",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "因为柳明秋已经死了，而死人是不会说话的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 638
    }
